Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The user class keeps track of the albums associated with this user and does bookkeeping for those albums.
    Author:
    Evan Loriot, Joseph Klaszky
